# Gleam Project Management
gleam new <project_name> - Create a new Gleam project
gleam run               - Compile and run the project
gleam test              - Run the project's tests
gleam build             - Build the project without running

# Gleam Dependencies
gleam add <package_name> - Add a new dependency
gleam remove <package_name> - Remove a dependency
gleam update            - Update all dependencies

# Gleam Tools
gleam format            - Format all Gleam source code in the project
gleam shell             - Start a shell with the project's dependencies available
